title: @OspreyWTEN Wraps up Play at Bedford Cup
text: dropped her semifinals match, 4-6, 6-2, 10-7. Marielle Calderon dropped her match in the Singles B bracket, 6-3, 6-3. closed her weekend with two wins in the South Consolation B bracket, taking her first match 6-0, 6-3 and her second match 6-3, 6-3. The Ospreys are back in action next weekend in Athens, Ga., when they compete in the ITA Regionals.
